Author: slavicshiba
Text: damn this was a surprisingly sweet message to open :) thank you, and i hope you're doing alright <3

Author: catsrule821
Text: Im going through the exact same issue right now. I know your frustration and i think its really cool and strong of you to go out despite this. My experience with being unable to fit into my clothes has caused me to isolate myself a great deal. Youre very strong and give yourself some patience/ space to accept that you cant wear a winning outfit all the time!
